{"tid":1877170,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】湖北省新增 14840 宗，大部分為「臨床診斷」","createTime":"2020-02-13T00:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T00:43:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c3a2e9a3947b3fe0cc6cc92cdcf54b7ec70de1","tid":1877170,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:40:12.000Z","msg":"湖北省新增新型冠狀病毒肺炎病例14840例，數字急增，主要是國家衛生健康委在病例診斷分類增加「臨床診斷」，新增數字包含了臨床診斷病例13332例。<br />\n<br />\n全省新增病亡242例（臨床診斷135例）。累計48206例（臨床診斷13332例）。<br />\n<br />\n國家衛健委指，加入「臨床診斷」數字，是方便患者能及早按照確診病例接受治療，提高救治成功率。根據新方案，近期湖北省對疑似病例開展排查，訂正了診斷結果，而新就診患者亦會按照新的診斷分類判症。<br />\n<br />\n臨床診斷是指醫生對病人檢查，判斷病因以及決定治療方案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E7%9C%81%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E-14840-%E5%AE%97-%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%82%BA-%E8%87%A8%E5%BA%8A%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258C%2597%25E7%259C%2581%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E-14840-%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E8%2587%25A8%25E5%25BA%258A%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2596%25B7%2F&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=2c210f63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E6%25B9%2596%25E5%258C%2597%25E7%259C%2581%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25A2%259E-14840-%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E8%2587%25A8%25E5%25BA%258A%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2596%25B7%2F&h=fe50c31b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E7%9C%81%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E-14840-%E5%AE%97-%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%82%BA-%E8%87%A8%E5%BA%8A%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B7/</a>"},{"pid":"267721b14bc03581663b9fdac77afa42497bd727","tid":1877170,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:42:12.000Z","msg":"咁點解死亡人數都會爆升？安樂死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f207124f46a88e18860c6c1e25d6f8a47afe47c5","tid":1877170,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:43:51.000Z","msg":"支那數據 人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n一個屍袋裝三個細路都俾人影埋出黎"}]}